{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011CdH7trXtySRS2YruUMF2Q","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The bug: the cache key only includes `opts.team`, ignoring `includeArchived`. So when some other caller requests `getUsers({ team, includeArchived: true })`, its result (archived users included) gets cached under `users:<team>` — and the people picker's `getUsers({ team, includeArchived: false })` call gets that same cached entry. The 60s TTL is why refreshing after a minute clears it.\n\nLet me check the test and cache files to confirm the shape."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":419,"cache_read_input_tokens":19935,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":419},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"36b86266-be9d-401a-9e61-c27f0019a344","uuid":"5ddd70f8-6fb0-461d-90b6-8c8ff23eb176","timestamp":"2026-07-22T12:46:29.837Z","request_id":"req_011CdH7tnLPYxb7YLsM8Qmi7"}
